                            Completed travel card request form
                            
                        </li><li>Credit limit and ATM cash withdrawal</li><li>Recommendation for approval</li></ul></td><td class="alignTopLeft">RCM</td><td class="alignTopLeft">RCM</td><td class="alignTopLeft">N/A</td><td class="alignTopLeft">EE</td><td class="alignTopLeft">DFMS</td></tr><tr><td class="alignTopLeft">3.2.10.3 Provide Authorization</td><td class="alignTopLeft"><ul class="index"><li>
                            Completed travel card request form
                            
                        </li><li>Recommendation for approval</li></ul></td><td class="alignTopLeft">DTCC</td><td class="alignTopLeft">DTCC</td><td class="alignTopLeft">N/A</td><td class="alignTopLeft">EE, RCM</td><td class="alignTopLeft">DFMS</td></tr><tr><td class="alignTopLeft">3.2.10.4 Obtain Travel Card From Departmental Travel Card Coordinator</td><td class="alignTopLeft"><ul class="index"><li>
